@coralstone85 Let's be careful of each other's nasty westerly winds and avoid catching a cold.
When I see the sunrise, I think of you, and when I see the sunset, I miss you.
The gift of your voice is pleasant, makes me feel light, @faz3 and is a little shrewd.

