Your Highness Sheikh Hamdan, 

A mother of four with US custody is urgently appealing to the Dubai court this week for the return of her children. Diplomatic intervention could expedite their safe return to their family. The children face grave danger with the man named Ishmael, an absent father from their lives, who plans to abduct them to Afghanistan and Iran via maritime routes. Every moment is critical. Please consider this plea for swift action to protect these children.

Respectfully, 🙏

