@becksieblock It was definitely a special summer for Hamdan!!!
Hamdan knows very well that his family is his most important source of strength, his greatest source of happiness and the best mood booster. 
Family strengthens self-confidence and gives unconditional love. It is a solid pillar of strength and enables you to give your best. A family conveys values such as love, respect, trust, hope, care and good manners. These values are essential for personal development 💎💎💎💎
